"lecture des fichiers mis en cache."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../preferences.rst:176
msgid "Image Quality (Disk Only)"
msgstr "Qualité de l’image (disque uniquement)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../preferences.rst:176
msgid ""
"Quality of the image files used in disk cache. The higher compression can "
